title: Myanmar All In One 2D Results

api_list.name: 2D3D Calendar Database
api_list.description: This endpoint where you can retrieve all the previous information of 2D Results and 3D Results with outputting 30 different results.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://myanmar-all-in-one-2d-results.p.rapidapi.com/api/v1/calendar"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "myanmar-all-in-one-2d-results.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
